    <scopecontent>
      <head>Scope and Content Information</head>
      <p>This collection largely consists of the official minutes of
         the Executive Committee of, and of the Board of Directors of
         the Virginia Council. Also included are financial statements,
         as submitted to the Executive Committee or the Board,
         committee reports, some general correspondence of Board
         members and other, miscellaneous items such as brochures,
         reports, etc., and copies of the By Laws in various revisions.
         The collection provides an excellent source for the study of
         the VCHR, and is useful for civil rights and related
         subjects.</p>
    </scopecontent>
